# RANK-AND-RENT SITE BUILDER

When I say **"build a new site"**, **"new site"**, or invoke this rule, run this entire
pipeline. Do not skip phases. Do not ask me to run separate prompts.

## REFERENCE LIBRARIES

- Competitors: `C:/Users/antho/OneDrive/Attachments/Documents/GitHub/Competitors/`
  — saved competitor sites organized by niche (e.g. `water-restoration/`), each niche
  containing `site-1/`, `site-2/`, …
- Designs: `C:/Users/antho/OneDrive/Attachments/Documents/GitHub/Design/`
